<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc9a9ead5-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s31i"><num value="31i">§ 31i.</num><heading> Report on resource research activities</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Once every five years the National Academy of Sciences shall review and report on the resource research activities of the Survey.</p>
